{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"19d490131c","title":"在击落美军无人驾驶飞机的报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e0b508c34c","index":0,"year":1964,"month":11,"day":22,"articleId":"19d490131c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"a597f697a3","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中国人民解放军空军司令员刘亚楼1964年11月22日为报送关于击落美军无人驾驶飞机的报告给中共中央办公厅警卫局局长江东兴的信上。信中说，特呈上报告一份，请口头转报主席，或者呈主席一阅。如有指示，请告知我们。"},{"id":"c92c007cde","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国人民解放军空军司令员刘亚楼、政治委员吴法宪、副司令员吴富善、副司令员兼参谋长张延发1964年11月20日关于击落美军无人驾驶飞机给毛泽东的报告。报告简要介绍了我空军1964年11月15日在广东遂溪地区击落美国军用无人驾驶高空侦察机的经过，并对这次高空平流层作战作了初步总结。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f6e4e4f764","type":"title","text":"在击落美军无人驾驶飞机的报告上的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c"},{"id":"a597f697a3","type":"paragraph","text":"亚楼同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c"},{"id":"c92c007cde","type":"paragraph","text":"此件以已阅，很好。闻你惠病，十分挂念。一定要认真休养，听医生的话，不可疏忽","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c"},{"id":"dbf82c5d56","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c"},{"id":"8e7cdd383b","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c"}],"page":{"id":"7f6269faa2","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"19d490131c","start":260,"end":260}}}},"__N_SSG":true}